Run native test runners (cargo test, go test, bun test, etc.)

Usage: normalize tools test [OPTIONS] [ARGS]... [COMMAND]

Commands:
  run   Run tests (default)
  list  List available test runners
  help  Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Arguments:
  [ARGS]...  Additional arguments to pass to the test runner

Options:
  -r, --root <ROOT>      Root directory (defaults to current directory)
  -R, --runner <RUNNER>  Specific test runner to use (cargo, go, bun, npm, pytest)
      --json             Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>        Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty           Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact          Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help             Print help
